# Architecture

Never duplicate logic.

Never duplicate state.

Never duplicate API calls.

Never duplicate validation.

Never duplicate constants.

If similar functionality already exists:

Reuse it.

If multiple screens need it:

Extract it.

Every component should have a single responsibility.

Every hook should have one purpose.

Business logic does not belong inside UI components.

Move reusable logic into hooks or utilities.
